{"abstract": "https://confengine.com/agile-india-2016/proposal/1793", "description": "This is about agile \u201canti-patterns\u201d: \u201csomething that looks like a good idea, but which backfires badly when applied\u201d (Coplien). Todd has been around agile development from before it was called agile.  In that time, he\u2019s seen teams fall into the trap of many of these anti-patterns, becoming stuck without ever realizing it. Frequently, this is due to a dogmatic understanding of what is right and wrong about Scrum and agile development. The first step to getting unstuck is to be able to detect these \u201csins.\u201d The presentation aims to expose teams to these common pitfalls and then also provide a vision for a virtuous path to take them to the Promised Land.", "event": {"name": "Agile India 2016", "nickname": "agile-india-2016", "twitter": "agileindia", "url": "http://2016.agileindia.org/"}, "favorite": "0", "file_date": "2016-12-03", "filename": "7-sins-of-scrum-and-other-agile-antipatterns-by-sean-dunn-chris-edwards", "length": "47:37", "likes": "1", "recorded": "2016-03-14", "short_description": "This is about agile \u201canti-patterns\u201d: \u201csomething that looks like a good idea, but which backfires badly when applied\u201d (Coplien). ", "speaker_twitters": " @chrisedwardsuk @SeanDunn10", "speakers": {"chris-edwards": {"episodes": [], "hosting": [], "info": {"country": "Canada", "home": "http://chrisedwardsuk.blogspot.com/", "name": "Chris Edwards", "twitter": "chrisedwardsuk"}, "videos": [{"event": {"name": "Agile India 2016", "nickname": "agile-india-2016", "twitter": "agileindia", "url": "http://2016.agileindia.org/"}, "filename": "7-sins-of-scrum-and-other-agile-antipatterns-by-sean-dunn-chris-edwards", "recorded": "2016-03-14", "thumbnail_url": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/FghQVc747Z4/hqdefault.jpg", "title": "7 Sins of Scrum and other Agile Antipatterns"}, {"event": {"name": "Agile India 2016", "nickname": "agile-india-2016", "twitter": "agilei